CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 5, 1958, pg. 4 reads: "10. Tom Hawkins and Ruth Higgins of Carnation Milk Company watches the 11. interesting stage display of Carnation by several small children at one session of the fair."
TitMainTitle: Tom Hawkins standing in Carnation Milk booth in Syria Mosque for the 1958 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
